room_title: Escape room "Apocalypse" by Trapped! Escape Room in Cleveland
review: Loved it. We did the apocalypse room. Lots of fun and the puzzles were interesting. We finished the room with 12 minutes left. We will definitely be back.

room_title: Escape room "Apocalypse" by Trapped! Escape Room in Cleveland
review: Tried out the new Apocalypse room yesterday and I had a blast! I really enjoy challenges like these and testing out my problem-solving skills within a group of people. I think next up is the Pirate room! See you soon, Trapped!

room_title: Escape room "Apocalypse" by Trapped! Escape Room in Cleveland
review: This was our first escape room. We weren't sure what the expect, but we had a blast at Trapped! We completed the Apocalypse. It was challenging, but so much fun. By the way, we escaped and saved the human race! We're discussing which room to tackle next.
